---

Sel01-Tweaker orchestrates and reimplements functionality from several
open-source projects. It bundles no third-party code; the orchestrated tools
(Win11Debloat, RemoveWindowsAI) are downloaded and run as-is at runtime, and
winutil-style tweaks and the RAM cleaner are independent reimplementations.
See NOTICE.md for full third-party attribution and license details.

DISCLAIMER: This software modifies Windows system settings. It creates a System
Restore point and a per-value registry backup, and provides a -Revert option,
but it is provided without warranty. Use at your own risk; test before relying
on it for production machines.
